POST {{base_url}}/api/deals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "titre": "Mon super deal",
  "description": "Deal incroyable à ne pas manquer !",
  "prixDeal": 1200.00,
  "prixPart": 12.00,
  "nbParticipants": 100,
  "dateDebut": "2026-02-09T10:00:00",
  "dateFin": "2026-12-31T23:59:59",
  "dateExpiration": "2026-12-31T23:59:59",
  "categorieUuid": "59682a41-7f68-480d-bb30-ebd04306948d",
  "categorieNom": "POISSON",
  "createurUuid": "eba8247c-a41c-4929-80e5-233a0677244e",
  "createurNom": "Jean Doe",
  "statut": "BROUILLON",
  "ville": "Alberta",
  "pays": "Canada",
  "listeImages": [
    "image1.jpg",
    "image2.jpg"
  ],
  "listePointsForts": [
    "Point fort 1",
    "Point fort 2",
    "Point fort 3"
  ]
}

### 2. Récupérer tous les deals (GET)
GET {{base_url}}/api/deals
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Récupérer un deal par UUID (GET)
GET {{base_url}}/api/deals/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Content-Type: application/json

